org.cougaar.core.thread
Class Scheduler

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.thread.Scheduler
Direct Known Subclasses:
PropagatingScheduler, RightsPropagatingScheduler
public class Scheduler
extends java.lang.Object

The base class of thread-scheduler. It allows a certain maximum number of threads to running, queuing any requests beyond that. An items is dequeued when a running thread stops. The maximum is per thread-service, not global. This scheduler is not used by default (the PropagatingScheduler extension is the default).
